.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-10::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: coffee, juice, lemonade, tea
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: june, october, november, september
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, egyptian, indian, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, biathlon, sailing, volleyball
1. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person drinking juice##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the left of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person drinking coffee is on the far left##1
4. the person drinking lemonade is the person who's birthday is in september##1
5. the person drinking tea is on the left of the egyptian##1
6. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
7. the malaysian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
8. the person who's birthday is in october is the person drinking tea##1
9. the argentine is on the right of the person who's sport is volleyball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
| Beverage      | coffee     | tea           | juice    | lemonade    |
| Birthday         | november  | october | june  | september |
| Nationality   | indian     | argentine     | egyptian | malaysian   |
| Sport         | volleyball | badminton     | biathlon | sailing     |

